title: Pick Your Best Memes
body:
# Preface
I announced like:
> **MEME CONTEST**
> Create any creative meme about LevX DAO and share it in 🌈meme-contest 
> 
> According to the result of a community vote, 3 winners will get 3.33 LEVX each.
> 
> Submission: 3 max per each
> Deadline: Oct 21 15:00 UTC
> I'll first pick 10 items and put a proposal in snapshot for community vote
> If you steal it from others, you'll be excluded from any opportunity to get any LEVX in the future + become a Jerry(Jerrys can never chat in any channel but in his own voice channel). 

# Applications
We got 200+ applications from 100+ Mortys.

# Election
Now it's your turn to pick best memes. Be careful about you choice: top 3 winners will get 3.33 LEVX each.
*⚠️ This is not a single choice vote, so you need to rank those from 1st to 10th.*
